-- Libery to Start Ghana Building This Year, Bus. Day Says
-- B y   S t e p h e n   G u n n i o n
-- 2012-05-04T05:35:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-04/libery-to-start-ghana-building-this-year-bus-day-says.html
Liberty Holdings Ltd. (LBH) ’s property unit
may start construction on two mixed-use property projects in
Ghana worth more than $100 million in the third quarter of this
year, Business Day reported, citing Samuel Ogbu, chief executive
officer of Liberty Properties.  The company, which is also working on projects in Nigeria’s
capital, Abuja, and Lagos, may expand into industrial property,
the Johannesburg-based newspaper cited Ogbu as saying.  To contact the reporters on this story:
